{
  "id": "69b9bbe1883354604c93c61d",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:バカの一つ覚えな展開",
  "created": 1773779965,
  "updated": 1773779979,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b9bbe1883354604c93c61d",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:バカの一つ覚えな展開",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779965,
      "updated": 1773779965
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfd0000000000a2213d",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779965,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2213e",
      "text": "「はいはーい、今日のテーマは『[バカの一つ覚えな展開]』ね！要するに、“またそれかよw”ってなるやつ。アニメでもゲームでもありがちじゃん？まずは軽く思いつくやつ出してこー」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2213f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22140",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22141",
      "text": "「そうですね……同じ調べを何度も奏でるような、安心感と、少しの退屈が同時に訪れる展開でございますね。（微笑）たとえば、物語の終盤で“実は主人公には特別な力がありました”と明かされるような……」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22142",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22143",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22144",
      "text": "「いわゆる“テンプレート依存”の構造だね。再現性が高い反面、サプライズは減衰する。RPGでいうと“最後に覚醒イベントが入る”のは典型例」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22145",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22146",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22147",
      "text": "「それそれ！覚醒イベ、もはや義務教育レベルw でもさ、嫌いじゃないんだよね。むしろ来たら“キター！”ってなるときもあるし」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22148",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22149",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2214a",
      "text": "「ええ、繰り返しには不思議な安らぎがございますもの。同じ物語の型に身を委ねることで、読者は迷わず感情を重ねられるのでしょうね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2214b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2214c",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2214d",
      "text": "「同意。ただし“過剰最適化”すると問題が出る。つまり、過去にウケた構造をなぞりすぎると、差別化が失われる。結果、作品間の識別性が低下する」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2214e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2214f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22150",
      "text": "「出た、りかのガチ分析w でもわかる。どの作品見ても“なんか前も見たな…”ってなるやつね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22151",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22152",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22153",
      "text": "「ですが、繰り返しの中にも微かな違いがございますよね。たとえば、同じ“記憶喪失の再会”でも、語られる言葉や間合いによって、まるで違う情景になることも……（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22154",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22155",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22156",
      "text": "「そこが“バリエーション設計”だね。同じプロットでも、キャラクターのパラメータや文脈を変えることで新規性を確保する。料理でいうと、同じレシピでも調味料の比率で味が変わる」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22157",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22158",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22159",
      "text": "「おー、わかりやすい！つまり“使い回し＝悪”じゃなくて、“使い方が雑だとバレる”って感じ？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2215a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2215b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2215c",
      "text": "「正確。あと、視聴者側の“学習”も影響する。一度パターンを認識すると、次からは予測が働く。予測を裏切るか、期待通りに気持ちよく当てるか、その設計が重要」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2215d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2215e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2215f",
      "text": "「期待を裏切るか、応えるか……まるで物語と読者が静かに対話しているようで、趣深いですね。（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22160",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22161",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22162",
      "text": "「でもさ、裏切ろうとしてグチャるやつもあるじゃん？“え、それやる必要あった？”みたいな」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22163",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22164",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22165",
      "text": "「ある。いわゆる“サブバージョン失敗”。前提条件の積み上げが不足したまま反転すると、説得力が崩壊する。結果、ただのノイズになる」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22166",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22167",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22168",
      "text": "「積み重ねがあってこその転調……まるで和歌のようでございますね。序と破があって、はじめて急が美しく響く……」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22169",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2216a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2216b",
      "text": "「急に雅w でもいい例え！結局さ、“バカの一つ覚え”って言われるかどうかって、“ちゃんと仕込んでるか”と“見せ方うまいか”にかかってる感じ？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2216c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2216d",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2216e",
      "text": "「要点を整理するね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2216f",
      "text": " 1. テンプレ展開自体は悪ではない（再現性・安心感がある）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22170",
      "text": " 2. 問題は差別化不足と過剰反復",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22171",
      "text": " 3. 成功の鍵はバリエーション設計と前提の積み上げ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22172",
      "text": " 4. 予測のコントロール（裏切る or 満たす）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22173",
      "text": "この4点」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22174",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22175",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22176",
      "text": "「とても明瞭でございますね。（微笑）どこか同じ物語に帰ってくるような心地よさと、新しい景色に出会う喜び……その均衡が大切なのでしょう」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22177",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22178",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a22179",
      "text": "「よーし、まとめると！“またこの展開かよw”って言われるか、“やっぱこれよ！”って言われるかは紙一重！ってことね。クリエイター、がんばれ案件〜」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2217a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2217b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2217c",
      "text": "「結論としては、“愚かに見える反復も、設計次第で武器になる”。以上」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2217d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2217e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bbfe0000000000a2217f",
      "text": "「ええ……繰り返しの中にこそ、創意は宿るのでしょうね。（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779966,
      "updated": 1773779966
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bc000000000000a22180",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779969,
      "updated": 1773779969
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9bc010000000000a22181",
      "text": "#2026-03-18",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773779969,
      "updated": 1773779979
    },
